column3: Provides no Influence. Agents here may not be added to the Squad this month but have their Wounds healed.
Provides no Influence. Agents here may not be added to the Squad this month but have their Wounds healed.
Eliminate one of your Agents stationed here to gain 3 Cubes.
The difference in POW between Agents stationed here must be 5 or more.
Upset: The first time each Campaign you station only one Agent here, that Agent becomes a Captain, removing the title from another Agent (your choice).
Upset: Any Agents stationed here are returned to the HQ and replaced with random other Agents from your HQ.
Only Avengers may be stationed here.
This Location only provides Influence if exactly one Agent is stationed here.
Only Agents with 0 or less POW may be stationed here.
To station Agents here, at least one of them must be a member of the Fantastic Four.
Only 3-cost Agents may be stationed here.
You only gain Influence from this Location if you station no Agents here.
The first time you station an Agent here each Campaign, gain a Clone of that Agent.
If you fully occupied this Location last month, you may not station Agents here this month.
Agents that cost 1, 2, or 3 cannot be stationed here.
Upset: If this Location is not fully occupied, receive 1 random Intel.
Agents stationed here have a 50% chance of being Wounded.
Agents stationed here have a 50% chance of being able to join your Squad this month.
You may only station Agents here up to the number of Agents in your Grave (max 4).
Regroup: Two of your Agents are stationed here from HQ. (Ego's Choice)
Agents stationed here are replaced with random Mercs this month.
Agents stationed here cannot be stationed next month.
Only Spider-Man's Rogues Gallery may be stationed here.
Upset: The first time each Campaign you station Agents here, one of them transforms into a Clone of Hulk.
Upset: Agents stationed here are revealed to your opponent.
Upset: Eliminate any Wounded Agents stationed here.
1-cost Agents cannot be stationed here.
At least 1 Agent stationed here must be 1-cost.
Ongoing Agents may not be stationed here.
Agents cannot be stationed here during December, January, or February.
Only On-Reveal Agents may be stationed here.
All Agents stationed here must have the same cost.
Only Move Agents may be stationed here.
On-Reveal Agents may not be stationed here.
Regroup: Any Agents you stationed here last month are placed here again this month.
Agents stationed here must added to your Squad this month or be Eliminated.
Upset: You may station an additional Agent here. If you fully occupy this Location, gain no Influence from it.
This Location cannot be viewed by your opponent for any reason, unless Raided.
Up to 4 Agents may be stationed here, but Agents may only be stationed here if they cannot be stationed elsewhere.
If you fully occupy this Location, destroy a random other Location.
Upset: A random Agent stationed here will return to HQ.
Upset: Your opponent receives Clones of Agents stationed here as Mercs this month.
Your opponent may add Agents stationed here to their Squad this month. You may not add them to your Squad this month.
Only 0 and 1-cost Agents may be stationed here.
Regroup: This Location's effect becomes a copy of a random other Location you own this month.
Upset: You may station 4 Agents here to gain 2 Influence. If you do so and station fewer total Agents than the opposing Faction, lose 1 Influence instead.
Upset: Units stationed here with 8 or less POW receive a Wound.
Agent(s) you station here must have the highest POW of your stationed Agents.
Upset: The first time you fully occupy this Location this Campaign, reveal the Location of one of the Infinity Stones.
This Location stations 4 Agents. If you fully occupy this Location, gain 1 Cube.
Upset: Agents stationed here receive a Wound.
Upset: You may station one Agent from your Grave here, ignoring space restrictions. If you add it to your Squad this month, remove it from the game after the battle.
Agents stationed here must have 6 or more POW.
Upset: If this location is not fully occupied, you may transfer Agents here from your HQ or other owned Locations.
Agents with 5 or more POW may not be stationed here.
Upset: If you fully occupy this Location, both Factions gain 1 Merc this month.
Upset: If you fully occupy this Location, both Factions gain 2 Mercs this month.
Only Ongoing Agents may be stationed here.
SHIELD may only station Villains here. HYDRA may only station Heroes here.
Only 6-cost Agents may be stationed here.
Upset: The first month this Location is not fully occupied, both Factions gain 5 Influence.
Agents with more than 2 POW stationed here cannot be added to your Squad this month.
Upset: Swap Agents stationed here with random Agents stationed in your other Locations.
Upset: If more than one Agent is stationed here, both receive a Wound.
Upset: Upset: Add an Agent here from HQ, exceeding space limits.
If you do not possess an Infinity Stone, Agents cannot be stationed here.
Upset: For every space here not occupied, a random stationed Agent you control receives a Wound.
Wounded Agents may not be stationed here.
Agents with 2 or less POW stationed here receive a Wound.
Upset: You may pay 2 Influence to heal the Wound of an Agent stationed here.
Upset: Agents stationed here are also considered stationed in a random other Location (exceeding space limits).
Only one Agent stationed here may be added to your Squad this month.
Any Agent stationed here may be added to your Squad this month, even if returned to HQ or restricted by another game effect.
Swap this Location with a random other Location, transferring any Agents in each to the new Location. These Locations transfer ownership, if you did not own them prior.
Upset: Agents stationed here are randomly sent to other Locations you own with available space.
Gain no Influence from this Location if more than 10 Agents remain in your HQ.
Upset: Agents stationed here are moved to the next Location you own with available space (excluding Medbay). Then, two random Agents from your HQ are stationed here.
4, 5, and 6-cost Agents may not be stationed here.
Regroup: The first month you own this Location, gain a free Recruit.
Regroup: One of your random Agents is selected. That Agent cannot be stationed this month, but the Agent's Wounds are healed.
A random Agent stationed here will activate its Character Ploy this month, in addition to the regular one.
Only Agents with lower POW than their Cost may be stationed here.
Upset: This Location stations 4 Agents. If you fully occupy this Location, a random 6-cost Merc is added to your Squad this month. (if one is available).
Only your starting Agents may be stationed here.
This Location only stations 1 Agent. That Agent must be a Captain.
Agents may not be stationed here. Provides Influence for free.
SHIELD may only station Heroes here. HYDRA may only station Villains here.
Gain 1 additional Influence for each Captured Agent stationed here.
Only Captains may be stationed here.
Upset: If this Location is not fully occupied, both Factions gain 1 additional Influence this month.
At least 1 Agent stationed here must be 6-cost.
If this location is fully occupied, both Factions receive -1 Influence this month.
Upset: If this Location is fully occupied, you may repair another of your Locations for free.
The first time each Campaign you station Agent(s) here, one of those Agents must be Eliminated.
Agents stationed here are immune to Character Ploys this month.
If you fully occupy this Location, Agents in this Location and a random enemy Location cannot be added to their respective Squads this month.
If more than one Agent is stationed here and their POW is not equal, the Agent(s) with the lowest POW are Wounded.
This Location only provides Influence if Agents stationed here are Vanilla.
Upset: Swap Agents stationed here with random enemy stationed Agents this month.
Regroup: This Location has the effect of a random other Location this month.
Regroup: Destroy one random other Location.
Gain 1 Influence for each Agent stationed here.
If fully occupy this Location, gain a random Free Agent as a Merc. You must add that Merc to your Squad this month.
If you station Agent(s) here, you must add a Clone of Sentinel to your Squad this month.
Upset: If you do not fully occupy this Location with exclusively 3 or 4-cost Agents, destroy this Location.
Regroup: One random Agent will be stationed here. (Krakoa’s Choice).
You must fully occupy this Location (if possible).
Only Vanilla Agents may be stationed here.
To station Agent(s) here, at least one must be one of the Guardians of the Galaxy.
Agents stationed here may not be added to your Squad this month. If you fully occupy this Location, gain a random Merc.
Upset: Agents stationed here move to random other Locations.
When one of your Agents would move to another Location, it moves to this Location instead, exceeding space limits (max 4).
This Location stations three Agents.
To station two Agents here, the combined total power must be 7+.
This Location has no effect.
Upset: If you fully occupy this Location, both Factions gain 3 additional influence this Month.
This Location stations up to 4 Agents. Only 1-cost Agents may be stationed here.
This Location stations up to 3 Agents. If this Location is fully occupied, the last Agent stationed is Wounded.
If no Agents are stationed here, revive a random Eliminated Agent here until the end of the month.
Upset: In September, destroy this Location and eliminate any Agents stationed here.
Upset: Agents are not considered stationed here until after this effect resolves.
Station two cards here. Draft a card.
If you clear this section, eliminate a random free agent.
